</div>

<p class="mt-4">For the characters we knew we wanted our own spin on fantasy type creatures. The main character started out as a simple slime but evolved into an animal mixed with plants, a design choice which bled into other characters.</p>
<p class="mt-2">Check out our character concepts here:</p>
